@{
    ViewBag.Title = "About Us | Trip Pakistan";
}

<!-- SUB BANNER -->
<section class="section-sub-banner awe-parallax bg-9">
    <div class="awe-overlay"></div>
    <div class="sub-banner">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="text text-center">
                <h2>ABOUT TRIP PAKISTAN</h2>
                <p>eXplore Pakistan With Us</p>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>

</section>
<!-- END / SUB BANNER -->
<!-- ABOUT -->
<section class="section-about">
    <div class="container">

        <div class="about">

            <!-- ITEM -->
            <div class="about-item">

                <div class="img owl-single">
                    <img src="/assets/images/about/Badshahi-Mosuqe.jpg" alt="">
                    <img src="/assets/images/about/pakistan-monument.jpg" alt="">
                </div>

                <div class="text">
                    <h2 class="heading">ABOUT Trip Pakistan</h2>
                    <div class="desc">
                        <p>Trip Pakistan newly established Travel and Tourism Company based in Lahore. We are offering travel services within Pakistan to eXplore Pakistan</p><br />
                        <p>Providing all kind of Travel Services, i.e. Domestic ticketing,Hotel Booking in all Cities of Pakistan from South to North of Pakistan. Pick and Drop from airports to Hotels and back to Airport in all cities of Pakistan. Sightseeing in all Cities with pick and drop facilities.</p><br>
                        <p>
                            The Main Idea and purpose of Trip Pakistan is to show the world that, Pakistan in one of the beautiful Piece of Land in the world. Pakistan
                            is full of adventures and worthy sightseeing from South to North and East to West of Pakistan. from the coastal areas to Hilly areas of Pakistan.<br />
                            We want to offer services not only to Locals but to the People from abroad as well. We want to Show the every inch of our Beautiful Pakistan....<br />
                            "LETS EXPLORE PAKISTAN TOGETHER"
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
            <!-- END / ITEM -->
            <!-- ITEM -->
            <div class="about-item about-right">

                <div class="img">
                    <img src="/assets/images/about/img-2.jpg" alt="">
                </div>

                <div class="text">
                    <h2 class="heading">WHY GUEST CHOOSE TRIP PAKISTAN?</h2>
                    <div class="desc">
                        <p>It is a long established fact that a reader will be distracted by the readable content of a page when looking at its layout. The point of using Lorem Ipsum is that it has a more-or-less normal distribution of letters, as opposed to using 'Content here, content here', making it look like readable English. Many desktop publishing packages and web page editors now use Lorem Ipsum as their default model text, and a search for 'lorem ipsum' will uncover many web sites still in their infancy. Various versions have evolved over the years, <b>sometimes by accident, sometimes on purpose</b> (injected humour and the like).</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
            <!-- END / ITEM -->

        </div>

    </div>
</section>
<!-- END / ABOUT -->
